{"type": "article", "id": 46523, "title": "这个“有心”的小盒，想给传情加点趣味｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-10-25T23:20:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36127, "name": "Zupagrafika"}, {"id": 45007, "name": "Room One"}, {"id": 6244, "name": "双峰"}, {"id": 10600, "name": "SomeOne"}, {"id": 45008, "name": "OneDotZero"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 176, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171025181811gIVEqKZah71ynDvb.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Lovebox</h3><p>有了技术的加持，人们传递感情的方式或许可以变得更有趣——抱着这样的想法，法国设计师 Jean 在麻省理工学院留学期间，给异地的未婚妻设计了一个“传情盒”，表达自己的思念。当他的朋友 Marie 发现后，建议他在此基础上进行完善，并最终促成了 Lovebox 的诞生。这个木盒子外有一颗突出的爱心，当用户通过 App 发送文字讯息后，它就会转动起来，直到有人打开盒盖才会停止，同时文字也会显示在内部的屏幕上。值得一提的是，如果有人用手指拨动爱心的话，另一端操作 App 的用户就可以看到爱心雨出现在画面上。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lovebox/lovebox-a-simple-and-generous-way-to-send-love-mes\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 79 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182459tGBjszTlFpgZ8VN4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.428125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181849h3Mr6ECi1xZmt5s8.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710251818494Hkh0QL1MzdX7Sl8.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><br></p><h3>Modern East by Zupagrafika</h3><p>继粗野主义 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38162.html\">Brutal East</a> 之后，用做纸模的方式让人们认识建筑流派的波兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.zupagrafika.com/en.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zupagrafika</a> 又一次以前东德为灵感，推出了一套名为 Modern East 的模型。它包含九个东德现代主义风格的建筑，其中国际电影院（Kino International）还配有三张可替换的电影海报，让你做一回城市规划师。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.zupagrafika.com/zupamarket_modern_east.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 19 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181948ehT4KaAYUg7qypls.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829070\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181948U2lDu70x3pnW4KLF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181948IV5F8KBEXCWvcJrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181949w3ZpKlhBdfn9yzME.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.836047\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025181948q1u5QJjk6EMerghv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.822093\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Surface by Room One</h3><p>你听说过科技木或是工程木（engineered wood）吗？它指的是利用仿生学原理，经过科技手段对普通木材进行加工后得到的装饰材料。最近，英国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://roomone.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Room One</a> 利用它开发了一款名为 Surface 的无线音响，让装饰品与电器的界限变得模糊。Surface 的外观就像是一块更大且圆润的滑板，这种简约低调的感觉也营造出了一种反差：一旦发出声响，就能给先入为主误以为它只是装饰的人们带来惊喜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182003ZIYXNT56R1jSfHxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710251820039EcN8SaPMi2nhyFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710251820032HU9WCF3J8e4XKmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182003vfPErcSg3z8KFY9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.456790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Twin Peaks craft beer by Ben Kopp &amp; Keith Shore</h3><p>不久前，洛杉矶 Ace Hotel 的剧场举行了一场名为 <a href=\"https://festivalofdisruption.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Festival of Distruption</a> 的艺术节。这个为期两天的活动由著名导演大卫·林奇策划，并且邀请到了《双峰》的主创进行对谈。为了配合这个特别的主题，再加上今年《双峰》第三季的如约而至，身为剧迷的设计师 Ben Kopp 和 Keith Shore 与林奇合作，根据林奇提供的手稿，设计了限量版的啤酒包装。三款啤酒分别被命名为 Log Lady、Red Room 和 Damn Good Coffee，即便没有露脸，通过罐身上的标志性场景，人们依然能很快辨别出是哪些角色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182016o1OCks9nAlQbeV6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182034m3btw9Pid5CSc2on.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182016PcRkAdmiSr7NH4WX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182016FZvGa7MsgUmJolI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Spyscape by SomeOne</h3><p>明年去纽约的话，别忘记去曼哈顿看看一间名为 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/46427.html\">Spyscape</a> 的间谍博物馆。既然说的是总是和秘密打交道的间谍生活，SomeOne 和 OneDotZero 这两家咨询公司和博物馆自身的设计团队联手打造了一套试图勾起观众好奇心的视觉系统。这些残缺但依旧可辨识的字符（S 还很贴题地设计成了问号）就像是待解的谜题，激发观众的兴趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182210FsroRN1Ecwp9JVOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182210sy74ECcqWrQtP69n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182210j4VfRdrhAie0I8CS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182210W3ijZAvsmYpkR9wr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182210mbtEoqW0l6zidXpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rosh by Chris Dorosz</h3><p>想象一下，当颜料不再受到笔刷的限制，能够自由地组成绘画会是什么样？旧金山艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.chrisdorosz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chris Dorosz</a> 用这套名为 Rosh 的“雕塑画”给出了自己的见解。只有从特定角度欣赏，你才能从混沌中发现这些笔画其实刚好构成了人像。到 11 月 18 日之前，Dorosz 此次创作的四“张”半身像都会在纽约的 <a href=\"http://www.murielguepingallery.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Muriel Guépin Gallery</a> 进行展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182137kQNFvRf4enrmPb7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182137kCzgG1RZDF9H56h8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.508801\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182137H5QUtd7e0O9Xa4kx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182138N1XIBrU8ql5esJvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.360833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171025182138G0p8OaTQNhSJWqYA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501251\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}